Walt Disney&amp;#039;s Snow White And The Seven Dwarfs

Ripped using MPlayer 1.0rc1-4.1.2-DFSG-free from Debian Stable (Etch). The Vob file is from DVD disc 1 from the platinum edition. The Amazon link is below. The information on DVD disc 1 says:
Feature Running Time: Approx. 84 Minutes
Stock #22254
Rated &quot;G&quot; in the United States of America

The back of the case says:
Original theatrical Aspect Ratio
